{"abstract":[{"text":"The `Orange Business Tools`` theme is an Orange theme but tailored for some products with heavy UI.","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"],"type":"inheritsFrom","kind":"relationships"},{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"Usages","text":"Usages","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Some products may have heavy and very rich user interfaces with a lot of components and elements to displays and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with which users can interact. Thus for such products there are specific constraints of spaces and sizes, even if","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"these products must be Orange flavored."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"That is the reason why this team is created: a kind of ","type":"text"},{"code":"OrangeTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" but wih adjustments on some tokens like spacings and sizings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To get the theme:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Integration","text":"Integration","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To use this theme, inject it to your view using ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and get it through environment variable.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    @main","    struct YourApp: App {","        var body: some Scene {","            WindowGroup {","                OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeBusinessToolsTheme()) {","                    \/\/ Your root view","                }","            }","        }","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Theme-tuning","text":"Theme tuning","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The theme can be customized a bit for more flexibility thanks to ","type":"text"},{"code":"Tuning","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You just need to give a predefined tuning configuration at theme init to build the one you need.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To apply the tuning:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your theme tuning","    let tuning = Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true)","","    \/\/ Apply it to your theme","    let theme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: tuning)","    \/\/ Or in one line","    let theme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true))","","    \/\/ Or apply predefined tunings","    let orangeFranceTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeFrance)","    let orangeBusinessTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeBusiness)","    let maxitTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: Tuning.MaxIt)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Typography","text":"Typography","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue","text":"Helvetica Neue","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The Orange brand strongly relies on the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" font family. Thus each Orange brand should, or must, use it.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For iOS the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" font family is available at system level, so it is not needed to get it through external assets.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"By default an instance of ","type":"text"},{"code":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" uses as font family the token ","type":"text"},{"code":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", which is today ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use another font family, you will have to send the suitable token or the suitable font family.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, beware, iOS API relies also on the PostScript name of the font.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"To be sure of the value to use, look at the font book of your device.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is recommended to use the font raw tokens.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ The following instanciations work","    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme()","    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(family: OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault)","    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(family: \"HelveticaNeue\") \/\/ Which is PostScript name of the font","    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(family: \"Helvetica Neue\")"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue-Arabic","text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Because the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"text":" font family does not manage arabic alphabet but latin one, it is possible apply another font family to the theme like the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic"}]},{"text":". This font family assets can be retrieved through the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"PostScript name management has been implemented for this font family, thus the weight are managed and it is only needed to add the font assets to the project,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"register them and define the font family name to use.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(family: \"Helvetica Neue Arabic\")"],"syntax":"swift"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.17.0"}]}],"name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangebusinesstools\/orangebusinesstoolstheme"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange Business Tools"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:29OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools0bcD5ThemeC","title":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools"]]},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme\/init(family:tuning:)"],"generated":true}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/s16SendableMetatypeP","title":"Swift.SendableMetatype","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme/init(family:tuning:)":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Constructor of the OrangeBusinessTools theme with its own providers of tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It uses also the providers of charts colors from Orange theme ("},{"code":"OrangeThemeColorChartSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangebusinesstools\/orangebusinesstoolstheme\/init(family:tuning:)","role":"symbol","title":"init(family:tuning:)","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme\/init(family:tuning:)","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"family","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FontFamilySemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic010FontFamilyB5Tokena"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tuning","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tuning","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract6Tuninga"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}]},"ic_theme_orangebusinesstools.png":{"identifier":"ic_theme_orangebusinesstools.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/ic_theme_orangebusinesstools.png"}],"type":"image","alt":null},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangebusinesstools","title":"Theme Orange Business Tools","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange Business Tools theme is dedicated to applications with strong dimensions constraints.","type":"text"}],"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orangebusinesstools.png"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"https://brand.orange.com/en/brand-basics/typography":{"identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","url":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","title":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangebusinesstools\/orangebusinesstoolstheme","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The `Orange Business Tools`` theme is an Orange theme but tailored for some products with heavy UI."}],"role":"symbol","title":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A Swift "},{"code":"class","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to implement all tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"object oriented paradigm"}]},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme contract"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is not a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"final"}]},{"type":"text","text":" class, its type cannot be seen as "},{"code":"Sendable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSTheme","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/s8SendableP":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable","type":"unresolvable"}}}